{"tid":1161421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(引渡惡法?)  陶傑: 你冷待專制,  沒有用，專制也會上門找你","createTime":"2019-05-19T07:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T12:00:31.000Z","uid":134071,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"31fce78c5af872e15524f9c22b56206214052608","tid":1161421,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:36:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/posts/2678293495576490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftokit.channel%2Fposts%2F2678293495576490&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=924e4963\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/tokit.channel/posts/2678293495576490</a><br />\n<br />\n陶傑 Channel<br />\n20 小時 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n「我討厭政治」這樣的結論，是幼稚的。但這種論點，在許多香港人之間很流行。在蘭桂坊的酒吧，在IFC的咖啡座，當許多二三十歲的港女，閒談的話題，除了Zara的服裝、淘寶的飾物，或者大阪北海道的日本美食，你跟她們講時局的是非，她們一皺眉頭，以為很有性格，說：我討厭政治。<br />\n<br />\n當劉霞女士：一個無辜的中國女子，毫無法律依據，被家中軟禁經年，即使能出走外國，除了要低調生活，變相是換了弟弟被軟禁，如果你跟這種港女說：口口聲聲「依法治國」，他們多不講道理，而又多麼虛假？港女也一臉不屑，說：「不要講這個好嗎？我不懂、也討厭政治。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>一個社會走向專制，自己放棄了自由權利，靠的是這樣的愚眾。</strong>她討厭政治？她不知道：麪包比上個月貴了一元，她喜歡吃的那家日本小餐廳結了業，或者乘地鐵，票價又貴了，這一切都是政治。<br />\n<br />\n一九四九年，中國即將「解放」，上海許多企業面臨重大的決定：要不要逃去台灣或香港？那時有許多生意人選擇留下來，說：「毛澤東雖然來了，上海幾百萬市民，不也要吃飯？店舖不也要做生意？我們是生意人，不管政治，留下來，有什麼問題？」<br />\n<br />\n結果，少數的人跑了，多數人留下來，後來「公私合營」，要他們交出財產，然後，要他們跳樓自殺。北京市長陳毅天天上班就問：「今天有多少傘兵？」<strong>政治是一隻鬼，你討厭牠，沒有用，牠上門找你。</strong>"},{"pid":"68cd208dfd71563f1f6c4b7d03ba67dca2ac8fff","tid":1161421,"uid":134071,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:38:18.000Z","msg":"陶傑今次又唔抽水， 講真心話<br />\n<br />\n (雖然佢無點名引渡惡法.... 但佢之前係節目都詳細描述引渡惡法如何恐怖)"},{"pid":"46e27f4702d6389ca0304bb2cd6e1fa09e44b436","tid":1161421,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b5ff7628c876c1626173f69748355f5cf0cea7","tid":1161421,"uid":29726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0bc8f805419103364e76fd62b22de21a59bca0","tid":1161421,"uid":138233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:43:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fb1bf19d81d7abb41ac63250e3ba9a8d33b24b","tid":1161421,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T07:44:19.000Z","msg":"係&nbsp; 光明頂(16.05.2019), 陶傑直言&quot;引渡惡法&quot;係香港史上最大變局.<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/Pro881_13.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2FPro881_13.aspx&d=ywm3zvd%2FSAlFHYQsdiPdPcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=90eddcec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/Pro881_13.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"104a1c71ef68fdc11454bf4f49eadbef2029c10f","tid":1161421,"uid":105995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T08:33:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfa9d92a2f65caa70e8477ec15e00623d6678b5","tid":1161421,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:06:19.000Z","msg":"好文，真心香港唔再適合長住。難想像10年後的香港。"},{"pid":"b53332fc808ccba7461f0cd274d9330177c9b379","tid":1161421,"uid":37596,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"政治是一隻鬼，你討厭牠，沒有用，牠上門找你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0dd525e1fcb72606f16ffc354e345dbb4db685f","tid":1161421,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit